description: Vet and Dutch grow closers on a mission to make sure neighborhood buildings are clear. Meanwhile, Eph and Nora perform experiments on their new patients, and Kelly begins her search for Zack.
name: By Any Means

deck: The first encounter between Jim West and Dr. Miguelito Quixote Loveless.
description: James West is assigned to guard a professor who has discovered an explosive, but he fails when the professor is assassinated by a genius inventor who's manufactured the explosive and plans to use it to extort land from the California territory.
name: The Night the Wizard Shook the Earth

description: Gus and Vaun wage an attack on Palmer as Eph struggles to connect with Zack. Councilwoman Justine Faraldo vows to bring her extermination policies to the other boroughs.
name: Fort Defiance

description: The Avengers are challenged by the fully formed and incredibly powerful Squadron Supreme for a battle that will end with only one team as the victor.
name: Avengers' Last Stand

description: Eph and Nora finally see their lethal virus in action. Fet takes the security of Red Hook into his own hands while Dutch and Setrakian set off for Staten Island to question Fitzwilliam, Palmer's former body guard.
name: The Silver Angel

description: The Squadron Supreme has taken over the world, leaving the Avengers for dead. Unbeknownst to the Squadron and the rest of the world, the Avengers are in hiding and working out a new plan to save the planet and stop the Squadron once and for all.
name: Avengers Underground

description:
Proper Japanese Title: (Rindou no Onnanoko)

Daikichi Kawachi is a 30-year-old bachelor. He meets an unfamiliar girl named Rin while at his grandfathers funeral. He comes to find out that girl is his grandfathers illegitimate child. There is a palpable rift between Rin and the rest of the family.
name: The Rindou Flower Girl

description:
Proper Japanese Title: (Yubi Kiri Genman)

What kind of clothes should I get her? What about dinner? What do I do about school? Daikichi is swept away by one responsibility after another. On her first day of preschool, Rins expression shows worry as Daikichi walks away from her to go to work.
name: Pinky Swear

description:
Proper Japanese Title: (Daikichi no Kimeta Koto)

Daikichi returns to his parents home to find clues regarding Rins mothers whereabouts. Although Daikichis parents were against his becoming Rins guardian, they soften up because they cannot deny that it feels like they have a new grandchild.
name: Daikichi's Decision

description:
Proper Japanese Title: (Tegami)

Rin is enrolled in a new, local preschool and befriends a boy named Kouki. Koukis mother is a single parent who also happens to be very beautifula combination that causes Daikichis heart to skip several beats.
name: Letter

description:
Proper Japanese Title: (Daikichi wa Daikichi de Ii)

The day Daikichi will meet Rins mother finally arrives. However, he is completely shocked when he learns what Masako is really like. As they part ways, Masako makes a specific request to Daikichi.
name: Daikichi Should Stay Daikichi

description:
Proper Japanese Title: (Watashi no Ki)

Rin finally enters elementary school. Daikichi suggests planting a memorial tree for her. He wonders if Souichi had planted a tree for Rin after she was born. Though not his ideal solution, he seeks out Masako once more for answers...
name: My Tree

description:
Proper Japanese Title: (Naisho de Iede)

Daikichis cousin, Haruko, ran away from her home along with her daughter, Reina. After talking with Haruko, however, he realizes how strong she has become over the years. He wonders what it means to marrywhat it means to be family.
name: Secretly Leaving Home

description:
Proper Japanese Title: (Ojchan no Daiji)

Rins summer vacation has started. Daikichi decides to pay his respects at Souichis grave together with Rin. Upon seeing a rindou flower placed in an ink bottle at the gravestone, Daikichi deduces that Masako was there mere moments ago.
name: Grandpa's Precious Thing

description:
Proper Japanese Title: ! (Tai-f ga Kita!)

A large-scale typhoon is coming! When Daikichi goes to pick up Rin at the daycare center, he finds that only Rin and Kouki are still waiting there. The three go home together, although the kids are much more excited about the coming storm than Daikichi.
name: A Typhoon Came

description:
Proper Japanese Title: (Onaka no Kaze)

On the way back from the towns culture festival, Daikichi learns that Rin has a fever. Despite being encouraged by Koukis mother, Daikichi grows progressively more worried about Rin. He then realizes just how important Rin has become to him.
name: Stomach Flu

description:
Proper Japanese Title: (Hajime no Ippo)

A year has passed since Daikichi met Rin. He thinks about what it means to be a parent while he and Rin play at the park. He experiences firsthand just how wonderful it is to live with someone else.
name: The First Step
What Is Dead May Never Die

description: When the Turtles are whisked through time by apprentice Time Master Renet, they all must work together to defeat the evil Time Master Savanti Romero.
name: Turtles in Time
The Old Gods and the New

description: Jon is tested by the wildling king; Tyrion asks for his reward; Daenerys sails into Slaver's Bay.
name: Valar Dohaeris

description: Arya runs into the Brotherhood Without Banners; Jaime finds a way to pass the time.
name: Dark Wings, Dark Words

description: Dany hears the price; Jaime strikes a deal with his captors.
name: Walk of Punishment

description: The Night's Watch takes stock. Dany exchanges a chain for a whip.
name: And Now His Watch is Ended

description: The Hound is judged; Jon proves himself; Robb is betrayed.
name: Kissed by Fire

description: Four Houses consider make-or-break alliances. Jon and the Wildlings face a daunting climb.
name: The Climb

description: Dany exchanges gifts in Yunkai; Brienne faces a formidable foe in Harrenhal.
name: The Bear and the Maiden Fair

description: Dany meets the Titan's Bastard; King's Landing hosts a royal wedding.
name: Second Sons

description: House Frey joins forces with House Tully. Jon faces his most difficult test yet.
name: The Rains of Castamere

description: Joffrey challenges Tywin. Dany waits to see if she is a conqueror or a liberator.
name: Mhysa

description: King's Landing prepares for a wedding; Dany finds Meereen; the Night's Watch braces.
name: Two Swords
The Laws of Gods and Men
Snowing in Tokyo! Nana and NANA
Nobu Arrives in Tokyo! Nana's Song

description: Rigby ruins Mr. Maellard's fancy lunch, and now he or Benson has to write a letter of resignation.
name: Lunch Break

description: Five travels into the team's memories, uncovering many truths and one horrifying secret that will change Six forever.
name: Episode Six

description: Three's past becomes present while a new Android proves looks can kill.
name: Episode Seven

description: While Six takes on a terrorist, Four and One's attempts to stop him reveal two huge bombshells.
name: Episode Eight

description: Four revisits his past to prove his innocence while One's realization about his origins could change everything.
name: Episode Nine
